---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About JILBIT" description="The story and mission behind JILBIT: Jesus Is Lord, Believe It.">
  <section class="content-shell py-32">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500">Our Story</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-5xl tracking-tight text-zinc-900 md:text-6xl">About JILBIT</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg text-zinc-600">
      JILBIT began as a simple confession among believers who wanted one message to shape everything: Jesus is Lord.
      What started as local encouragement evolved into a ministry focused on outreach, discipleship, and gospel-centered action.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-shell py-24">
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80 p-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Why it matters</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-zinc-600">
        In a culture of noise and uncertainty, people need clear hope. We believe the message of Jesus brings identity, purpose,
        healing, and eternal direction.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
